text: Nasir Hossain (born 30 November 1991) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He is an all-rounder. He made his One Day International (ODI) debut in August 2011 against Zimbabwe. He also made his Test debut in 2011. The opposition team was West Indies. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:People from Rangpur Division
